These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, skateboarding, golf, cricket, rowing, sailing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Sport   | badminton | cricket | rowing | skateboarding | golf | baseball | sailing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, superhero, scientific, comedy, fantasy, disaster, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | fantasy | scientific | disaster | comedy | superhero | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, september, january, august, february, july, may
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in the middle##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Birthday   | february | november | july | january | may | september | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-4::.
House: wooden, townhouse, cottage, cape-cod, farmhouse, tower, gothic-revival
1. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the wooden house##1
3. the tower house is on the far right##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the tower house##1
5. the townhouse house is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7    |
| House   | gothic-revival | cape-cod | wooden | townhouse | cottage | farmhouse | tower |

