4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating banana##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Food   | carrot | pepper | banana | lemon | asparagus | potato | peach |

