3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |    3    |     4     |       5       |   6   |   7    |
| Pet   | goat | mouse | hedgehog | turtle | dog | rabbit | lizard |

