.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: tea, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea
1. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |    4    |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | iced-tea | soy-milk | tea | almond-milk | juice | hot-chocolate |

 